{"tid":1456982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣告散水撚又成功","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:30:51.000Z","uid":18354,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21eb41c7764a7344040b8da0201ec037e23dd505","tid":1456982,"uid":18354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"機場慢慢開始正常運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇live有員工指到境既人去到9點都未散到<br />\n<br />\n但我地就自己散左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個女仔右眼既怒火原來淨係值大家半日時間"},{"pid":"f8cbbd694fd1108a8e95951d9a98f3e59a3e08da","tid":1456982,"uid":18354,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:09:25.000Z","msg":"Be water 得好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51b5e4476094a42b8b80f1b783d5db5aeacbb87","tid":1456982,"uid":293698,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb22bf34874c10ea5b0461c1268cfc33537eb13c","tid":1456982,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得早兩日同琴晚，有班人出面包括連登開post搞出境今日先咁緊張，和理非主場冇需要亂放風有咩行動。"},{"pid":"863059b5e641c672ad38600005029896ea665ac1","tid":1456982,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"同721前晚勁似<br />\n<br />\n好多人屌散水撚 話前線自決<br />\n<br />\n結果721呢? 死傷慘重<br />\n<br />\n由尋晚可見 7月前線已經被滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家一大班分化撚同屌鬼撚就證明上面推論完全正確<br />\n<br />\n自己睇路 唔好唔記得尋晚就係班換衫黑鬼主動搞事清場<br />\n<br />\n今朝機場 周圍都係換衫黑狗"},{"pid":"88e15a0be6ea09260f772dbdebe00b3f945d805f","tid":1456982,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"咩叫半日時間，聽日唔可以再嚟？"},{"pid":"dbdcfe9b5d905afb4c5a34fa874d9e5605012081","tid":1456982,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4